Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:21:03.28,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}愉悦也好悲伤也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:10.05,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}将一切拥入怀中不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:24.41,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}那是将你我的手紧紧相连之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:28.88,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}指引我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:35.71,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}遥远的呼唤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:39.82,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}如同微笑一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:43.04,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}如同歌唱一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:50.13,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}是风儿在回响的声音
