Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  都搞散啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也有奇洛儿的圣诞蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢  让
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让里面能装满礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------TITLE-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:03:02.11,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,135)\fad(950,1050)}「…白色圣诞节。」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服是圣诞老人的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  每年藤本都会装扮成圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这活也只有我才能胜任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:03:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生还在生我的气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事  你应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖啊  金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正等你呢  干到这么晚辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我还很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你回家吧  要是你不觉得麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节到处闪闪发光的  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  你有什么想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经用义卖会上赚到钱买到了新玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我送你一个适合你的东西可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给我吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是圣诞节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦呢  明明是圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  圣诞节什么的和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  你和清和还没有和好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子我果然是被藤本先生讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生他和平常不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说刻薄的话了  连看都不看我一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小鸠没有错」  清和一定也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过他没有坦率的说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也会再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我等你  在托儿所门口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  天很冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里也是圣诞节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给猪尾吕义先生也准备礼物才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖  满满一瓶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我为猪尾吕义先生做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生变成驯鹿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天比平常要早呢  小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  要为圣诞大会准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠姐  今晚要是没有安排的话就来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要办圣诞晚会  妈妈下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  藤本哥要是方便的话也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的圣诞晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要打工  而且…圣诞节…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工要加油哦  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你们俩也快点出门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节明明大家都很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有藤本先生看上去很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为我之前多管闲事的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在平安夜这个日子变成了孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和的妈妈从那天起就再也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久以后清和就被清花的爸爸领养了
Comment: 0,0:10:43.89,0:11:12.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  开始开圣诞大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么藤本  等大家一叫你  你就进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你换好衣服就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生好伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好伟大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起来叫圣诞老人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  清和老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圣诞老人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人是清和老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位先生是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大家想向圣诞老人要什么礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人  礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家一起来吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去收礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来收拾杂物的工作就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  今天是圣诞节…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你操多余的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  为什么我要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗唆  圣诞节是旺季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…因为是圣诞节所以清和心情不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像反而伤害了藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被藤本先生讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…为什么会这么痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么在意清和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自觉地就会想到藤本先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不知为什么  一想到他  我的胸口就很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是送给小鸠你最好的礼物  我现在终于知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会  不是给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你能把这个送到在天文台的小鸠手上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  我替你打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  为什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是圣诞节  她看起来却很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是被你的态度伤到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小鸠认为这是她自己的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠她在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她独自一人在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没做错什么  用不着在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…你干嘛自己钻牛角尖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…莫非…  藤本先生没有生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说…我从一开始就没生过气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现…现在在生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…你别在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这是堂元要我送的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…  顺利和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我送你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这家伙欺负人了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生送我的礼物是藤本先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元跟你说了什么让你在这里等着？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说要去拿一个最适合我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是堂元先生让我和藤本先生和好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生  下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪也真是种很美的事物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样  等到冬去春来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要和土鸠分别了啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------NEXT-------------------
